          <li>Adhesive roller and paper roll with quick-change window structure — easy and fast maintenance</li>
          <li>Supports 4-layer, 8-layer copper foil board processing (4~12mil): 2-layer/1 pass, 4-layer/2 passes, multi-layer/3 passes</li>
